42#ifdef HAVE_CONFIG_H
43# include <config.h>
44#endif /* HAVE_CONFIG_H */
45#include <am_defs.h>
46#include <fsi_data.h>
47#include <fsinfo.h>
48
49
50static int
51write_dumpset_info(FILE *ef, qelem *q)
52{
53 int errors = 0;
54 disk_fs *dp;
55
56 ITER(dp, disk_fs, q) {
57 if (dp->d_dumpset) {
58 fprintf(ef, "%s\t%s:%-30s\t# %s\n",
59 dp->d_dumpset,
60 dp->d_host->h_lochost ?
61 dp->d_host->h_lochost :
62 dp->d_host->h_hostname,
63 dp->d_mountpt,
64 dp->d_dev);
65 }
66 }
67 return errors;
68}
69
70
71int
72write_dumpset(qelem *q)
73{
74 int errors = 0;
75
76 if (dumpset_pref) {
77 FILE *ef = pref_open(dumpset_pref, "dumpsets", info_hdr, "exabyte dumpset");
78 if (ef) {
79 host *hp;
80
81 ITER(hp, host, q) {
82 if (hp->h_disk_fs) {
83 errors += write_dumpset_info(ef, hp->h_disk_fs);
84 }
85 }
86 errors += pref_close(ef);
87 } else {
88 errors++;
89 }
90 }
91
92 return errors;
93}
